synthbio.files
Class BioBrickRepository

java.lang.Object
  synthbio.files.BioBrickRepository

public class BioBrickRepository
extends java.lang.Object

Read BioBricks from the provided csv files. For each kind of BioBrick, two methods are provided. One to fetch a collection containing al known bricks, and one to find one Brick by its name or transcription factor(s).
